Kugeza ku itariki ya 2 Werurwe 2020, iyi virusi imaze gutuma abantu barenga 80,000 bagerwaho n'icyorezo cya COVID-19, abarenga 40,000 barekuwe mu bitaro, ndetse abarenga 3,000 bahitanwa nacyo.
