Gukaraba intoki, nanone bita isuku y'intoki, ni imyitwarire yo gukaraba intoki kugira ngo umuntu akureho imyanda, amavuta, uturemangingo cyangwa ibindi bintu bitari ngombwa.
Gukaraba intoki mu gihe cy'umunsi mu bihe bimwe na bimwe by'ingenzi, bifasha kwirinda indwara nyinshi, urugero nko gutakaza amaraso n'indwara z'ibicurane.
