Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe umutekano mu kazi n'ubuzima (OSHA) kivuga ko imirimo itari myinshi n'abandi bakozi bakora mu kazi, ari imirimo itari ifite ubwandu bw'indwara, kandi ko hashyizweho ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda kwandura, harimo gukangurira abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, gukurikiza imikorere yo guhumeka no kohoka no gukora isuku n'ubwandu mu kazi.
Mu mirimo ishobora gutuma umuntu agira ubwandu bwa COVID-19 cyangwa se ikamuteza ubwandu, harimo n'imirimo ikenera guhura kenshi cyangwa hafi n'abantu batazi cyangwa bakeka ko bafite COVID-19, ndetse n'imirimo ishobora gutuma umuntu agira ubwandu kubera ubwandu rusange cyangwa ingendo mpuzamahanga.
Muri ibyo bikorwa harimo n'abanyeshuri, abakozi bahura n'abaturage muri rusange, nk'amashuri, ahantu hakorerwa imirimo y'akazi hakungahaye ku baturage, ndetse n'imimerere imwe n'imwe igaragaza ko ibicuruzwa byabo bikomeza kugurishwa cyane.
Uretse ibikorwa by'ibanze byo kwirinda icyorezo, hari n'ibindi byakozwe mu rwego rwo kugenzura akaga muri iki kipe harimo gukingira umwuka, guhumeka, gukoresha ibyuma bigabanya ubukana bikoresha ibipimo by'umwuka bikora neza, ndetse no kugira ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi ku giti cyawe mu gihe bikenewe mu mishyikirano bagirana n'umuntu urwaye COVID-19.
OSHA ivuga ko abakozi bakora mu buvuzi cyangwa mu bitaro bagaragara ko bafite COVID-19 cyangwa bakekwaho ko bafite COVID-19 bafite ibyago byinshi byo guhura na yo, kandi ko iyo ari abakozi bakusanya cyangwa bagakora ibipimo by'umurava ku bantu bakekwaho ko bafite COVID-19, cyangwa bakora udukoko dutemba mu kirere, bafite ibyago byinshi byo guhura na COVID-19.
Ibi byiciro by'ubugenzuzi bigenewe abakozi birimo ibipimo by'ubugenzuzi, urugero nk'ibyumba by'umwuka bifite umwuka mubi w'umushinga mubi, n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi ku giti cyawe bihuye n'intego y'akazi.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyagize ingaruka nyinshi ku kazi.
Abakozi bashobora kutaza ku kazi kubera uburwayi, gushaka kwita ku bandi cyangwa impungenge z'uko bashobora guhura na bo.
Imikorere y'ubucuruzi ishobora guhinduka haba mu buryo bw'ibintu bifuza no mu buryo bwo kubikura (urugero: kugura ibintu mu gihe umuntu atiriwe aterwa n'abantu benshi, cyangwa uburyo bwo gutwara ibintu mu rugo cyangwa serivisi zo kugura imodoka).
Mu gihe cy'ibihe bitandatu, ibicuruzwa by'ubwoko bw'igihugu by'u Rwanda bishobora gutangwa mu bihugu bifite ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bukabije, kandi bishobora gutangwa mu bihugu bifite ubwandu bukabije.
Imirimo ikora ku bintu by'ingenzi byatuma abakozi bagira ibibazo, urugero nk'ibyago byo guhura n'ibikoresho, ibyago byo mu kazi no mu ntego zitandukanye, ibyago bituruka ku rugo no mu muryango, n'ingaruka z'iza bukuru cyangwa indwara z'igihe kirekire.
Nanone kandi, izo nyandiko zigaragaza uburyo bwo kugenzura ibyo bibazo, kandi zishobora gushyiraho ingamba zo guhangana n'imimerere ishobora guterwa n'icyorezo.
Imyiteguro y'icyorezo n'ibikorwa byayo byakozwe hakurikijwe inama zatanzwe ku rwego rw'igihugu cyangwa ku rwego rw'akarere.
Mu byo bagamije kugira icyo bakora ku cyorezo harimo kugabanya ubwandu hagati y'abakozi, kwirinda abantu bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara, gukomeza ibikorwa by'ubukungu no kugabanya ingaruka mbi ku mihanda yabo yo gutumiza ibindi bikorwa.
Mu karere k'abaturage aho ibikorwa byakozwe, ubukana bw'indwara bugira ingaruka ku buryo umuntu agira icyo akora.
Ingingo z'ubuyobozi bw'ibyago ni ihame rikoreshwa cyane mu bijyanye n'umutekano n'ubuzima mu kazi, rigamije gushyiraho ingamba zo kugenzura ibyago mu buryo buhuje n'uko bikora.
Iyo nta cyo umuntu yakora ngo akureho icyorezo cya COVID-19, inzego z'ubugenzuzi ni zo zonyine zifite ubushobozi bwo kugenzura inganda, nyuma zikagenzura, amaherezo zikagenzura ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi.
Mu by'ubugenzuzi bw'ubuhanga, abakozi bagomba kuba baritandukanyije n'akaga k'akazi, nta gushingira ku bikorwa by'umukozi, kandi bishobora kuba ari byo byonyine byoroshye gushyira mu bikorwa.
Mu gihe umuntu afite inshingano yo kuyobora abandi, aba agomba kuba afite inshingano yo kuyobora abandi.
Nubwo ibikoresho byo kwirinda ubwonko (PPE) bitagira ingufu nk'iz'ubugenzuzi n'ubuyobozi, bifasha abantu kwirinda ibintu bimwe na bimwe.
Buri bwoko bw'imiti y'umubiri (PPE) buzajya bufatwa hakurikijwe ibyago byugarije abakozi mu kazi, bugashyirwa mu buryo bukwiriye (urugero, imyanya y'ubuhumekero), bugakoreshwa neza, bugasuzumwa buri gihe, bukomeze kubungabunga, bugasimburwa uko bikenewe, bukurwaho neza, bukorerwa isuku, hanyuma bukagurwaho nta n'umwe ugenda ku isonga.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo cy'ubuvuzi n'umutekano muri Amerika (OSHA) bwagaragaje ko akazi gafite ibyago bike byo guhura n'abantu benshi ndetse n'abandi bakozi, ndetse n'akazi gakora, ari ko gafite ibyago bike byo guhura n'abantu benshi.
Mu bikorwa by'ibanze by'ubudahangarwa byasabwe ku mirimo yose harimo gukaraba intoki kenshi kandi neza, guhamagarira abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe umunsi utameze neza, guhisha abantu ko bakonje cyangwa ko bahuma, gutanga imyanda no gushyira mu cyondo, gutegura cyangwa gutandukanya ahantu ho gukorera amakuru kure, kubuza abakozi gukoresha izindi gahunda n'ibikoresho, no gukomeza gukora isuku mu buryo buhoraho no kwanduza mu karere k'akazi.
Gushakisha abantu bafite ubwandu vuba no kubashyira mu kato ni intambwe ikomeye mu kurinda abakozi, abakiriya, abashyitsi n'abandi ku kazi.
Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) cyateye inkunga abakozi bafite ibimenyetso by'indwara z'ubuhumekero butunguranye ko bagomba kuguma mu rugo nibura amasaha 24 bataranywa imiti itera ibicurane cyangwa itera ibimenyetso by'ubushyuhe, ibimenyetso by'ubushyuhe bukabije, n'ibindi bimenyetso, kandi bagatuma amategeko y'ubuvuzi ahinduka, abakozi bashobora kwita ku bagize umuryango barwaye mu rugo, kandi abakozi bamenye amategeko yayo.
