Nyuma y'umwaka wa 2019, OMS yashyize ku murongo imibare y'abanduye SARS-CoV-2 yemewe n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi, mu gihe yashyiragaho imibare y'abanduye ICD-10 y'icyorezo, ikaba yashyize ku murongo imibare y'abapfuye ku SARS-CoV-2 U07.1, naho imibare y'abapfuye ku COVID-19 basanze mu bushakashatsi bw'ubuvuzi cyangwa mu bushakashatsi bw'indwara z'ibyorezo, aho nta gihamya y'ubuvuzi bw'ibigo by'ubuvuzi bw'ubuvuzi, ikavuga ko ari U07.2. Umubare w'abapfuye ku gihe runaka ugabanyijwemo umubare w'abapfuye ku gihe runaka.
Imibare yatanzwe na Johns Hopkins University igaragaza ko ku itariki ya 17 Mata 2020, umubare w'abapfuye ku isi wari 6.9% (153,822/2,240,191).
Ibipimo bitandukanye bitewe n'akarere: mu bindi bipimo harimo igipimo cy'ubwandu (IFR) kigaragaza umubare w'abantu bapfa bazize indwara (CFR) n'igipimo cy'abapfa bazize indwara (abafite iyo ndwara n'abatagira iyo ndwara).
Ibipimo by'abantu byerekana umubare nyawo w'abanduye, aho kuba igihe ntarengwa, bitewe n'uko ibintu byifashe neza.
